summary: This is the model of Isolde used in my bodyslide preset pictures.
descriptionHtml:
Not much to say other than that this is a copy of the character used here:Â https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89714

Requirements:

1. Racemenu
2. SKSE

To make her look exactly like the screenshots:

1. Custom Skin texture Mashup (The Diffuse of Mature Skin, the Normals of SRG, the goosebumps and Subscattering of Fair Skin, the makeup of SG)
2. The eyes of beauty
3. Sg eyebrows
4. SG hairpack 268 or 350

Installation:

Use 7zip or WinRar to unzip the file and place in Skyrim/data/skse/pluginsChargen/Presets
To delete, just delete the .jslot file.
author: Itstyle101
